Defendant Tobias A Rivera in court with attorney Adam J. Schleis.  Andrea M. Will appeared for the State of Wisconsin.  Defendant enters a guilty plea to Count 1.  Court finds defendant guilty.  Count #2 is dismissed and read in.  The Defendant was sentenced to the following:

IMPOSED AND STAYED SENTENCE OF:   

6 MONTHS, JAIL(CREDIT - 26 days);

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 YEAR(S); probation may be transferred to Milwaukee County; Defendant may report to Probation on Tuesday, October 27, 2015 no later than 3:30 p.m.;

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  

*Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
*Maintain full time employment and/or combination of schooling;
*Obtain GED or HSED;
*Write letter of apology to victim;
*40 hours community service at a rate of $10.00 per hour up to costs;
*Any other condition deemed appropriate by agent;

COURT COSTS:  $243.00 (apply cash bail, balance to be paid as a condition of probation);

The Court does not grant expunction.
